rmal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3931faf59dd4a0b59f4681ad1123a8861f179d","tid":1546640,"uid":36690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"手法好似無咁激進，似係知道自己奶左野所以收斂左"},{"pid":"64acf52752ab6ff59cea8c8982f231ce1f347dff","tid":1546640,"uid":272186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"個人基本上認為已有示威者被打死<br />\n港共近2日不斷製造假自殺隱瞞 可惜仲未有確實證據<br />\n<br />\n啲狗唔敢打人好大機會佢地都知道有示威者被打死<br />\n雖然佢係係無良知無腦嘅垃圾狗<br />\n但去到殺人呢個心理關口係好大<br />\n所以而家要煲大佢 仲要唔好畀佢地習慣殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f86b347c7d00877b60668528c3d285a1a32a46b","tid":1546640,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:07:23.000Z","msg":"我比較想知佢哋點處理屍體？<br />\n同埋失蹤成個禮拜<br />\n完全無屋企人出聲<br />\n呢吓點樣做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">無論最後開咩牌<br />\n我都心感佩服 做到完全滅聲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9cc76cde9e9201b88bbefe3d51001fd1ad97dd","tid":1546640,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"殺人填命 講多無謂<br />\n我地要贏喔喔喔喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想升級體力手足可參考下面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各做所長<br />\n營養＋運動 身心感覺同樣重要<br />\n唔係淨運動chur 死左仲點有力幫手<br />\n小弟做補師 大家同我頂住<br />\n集結正能量 我地要團結齊整地贏<br />\n決定想改變想學野就入黎<br />\n<br />\n借個位提升大家體力幫手長期行路/封鐵後點行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黎緊咩行動都要齊出</span></span><br />\n全民行動 健體惡補知識同黨鐵政府頂住<br />\n<br />\n和理勇武強身健體飲食入門：<br />\n香港人一定要贏<br />\nPOPO打無辜民市打到出面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要有自衞隊身體質素<br />\n鋪鋪封站要長途跋涉 <br />\n唔夠體力行唔到幫手😭<br />\n<br />\nStep 2. 補水 補電解質<br />\n飲夠水<br />\n每日飲體重x50ml水<br />\n每半個鐘每淡唔多過300ml<br />\n平日飲10個鐘<br />\n會去多廁所 但幫身體補水換水好緊要<br />\n電解質 補充成個人體液<br />\n保礦力稀釋5-10倍更有效吸收<br />\n就咁飲太高糖唔吸收<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\nHerbalife  健康教練<br />\n唔係重點 重點係大家強身健體<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民皆兵</span></span> <br />\n依家風頭火勢<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 團結 正能量<br />\n我要所有人隨時隨地可以極速轉場<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地可以更團結 去改變香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衝衝子走得快<br />\n哨兵Be Water <br />\nFirst aid 補給 <br />\n全世界只有你可以有能力保護自己同記者<br />\n有咩搵我幫手 免費教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需 要TG 唔問名 <br />\n同你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n如果想做下運動放鬆<br />\n歡迎黎搵我做下運動 <br />\n有街頭健身<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"5eb82efe615738b457ab893ce4b4bdb3e22af4d0","tid":1546640,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3d1b8351254fca5aaddc44334ac46258671b1e2","tid":1546640,"uid":64946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c198ae124e5fda5de2cedaf227cc4205399b77f","tid":1546640,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike"